        "formula": "令 N=64, C=128, L_in=65536, K=8, S=1, P=4。则输出长度 L_out = floor((L_in + 2*P - K) / S + 1) = 65537。对于 0 <= n < N, 0 <= c < C, 0 <= l < L_out，Y[n,c,l] = (1/K) * sum_{k=0}^{K-1} ( X[n,c, l*S + k - P] 若 0 <= l*S + k - P < L_in 否则为 0 )。",
